        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/miami/scene_flamingo.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 71c079af-329f-4fe1-a355-6b0aaf479d73).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47.\r\rThe Thwack teams&apos; head chef has just discovered that four very important guests have left one-star reviews on his catering. After slow roasting his beef brisket for 15 hours, this is the thanks he gets. \r\rFernando called his coleslaw &quot;mid&quot;. Maxwell described the brioche buns as &quot;soggy&quot;. Alsyen said the knife work looked &quot;nasty&quot;. And the Sheikh didn&apos;t even finish his dish. \r\rThe chef has resigned. But before he left, he did leave behind a request - and his favourite cleaver.",
